130
00:07:00,712 --> 00:07:02,130
Kenapa kamu datang seperti itu?

131
00:07:03,673 --> 00:07:04,549
Anda sedang libur kerja, kan?

132
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,593
Apakah Anda punya rencana?

133
00:07:07,552 --> 00:07:08,595
Bagus

134
00:07:09,971 --> 00:07:11,890
Baiklah kalau begitu, mari kita lanjutkan.

135
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,434
Ya? Oh, tiba-tiba di suatu tempat...

136
00:07:14,517 --> 00:07:16,061
