182
00:09:19,392 --> 00:09:20,685
eh? Mereka bilang ayam ada di sini

183
00:09:20,769 --> 00:09:21,686
Saya akan segera mengambilnya

184
00:09:22,896 --> 00:09:24,147
Simpan di sini.

185
00:09:25,273 --> 00:09:26,149
Ah, lewat sini.

186
00:09:26,232 --> 00:09:28,526
Saya perlu makan ayam di sini, jadi cepat simpan!

187
00:09:35,658 --> 00:09:36,618
'Orang itu'?

188
00:09:39,829 --> 00:09:41,790
[Klik] [Wanita] Wow, pemandangan malamnya indah sekali

189
00:09:41,873 --> 00:09:42,874
[Pria] Benar?

190
00:09:42,957 --> 00:09:46,419
Oh, maukah kamu pergi ke Jembatan Jamsu di sana saat Natal?

191
00:09:46,503 --> 00:09:47,796
Katanya di sana ada tempat kembang api yang terkenal.

192
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:49,130
- [Wanita] Aku menyukainya - Jembatan Jamsu?

193
00:09:49,214 --> 00:09:50,423
[Tawa pasangan]

194
00:09:50,507 --> 00:09:52,258
- [Pria] Ta-ta - [Wanita] Ta-ta

195
00:09:52,342 --> 00:09:54,260
