197
00:10:04,646 --> 00:10:07,565
Hei, kudengar ada kembang api yang dimulai pukul 7.

198
00:10:07,649 --> 00:10:09,234
Itu tidak bergerak.

199
00:10:11,069 --> 00:10:12,112
[mendesah]

200
00:10:12,195 --> 00:10:15,198
Berapa lama waktu yang dibutuhkan? Saya ada pertemuan penting.

201
00:10:15,281 --> 00:10:18,451
[Artikel] Jika Anda sedang terburu-buru, akan lebih cepat jika Anda menyeberang dengan berjalan kaki.

202
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:22,997
[Haran] Ya, Foto Yoon.

203
00:10:23,081 --> 00:10:24,874
Hawa sangat terhambat.

204
00:10:26,292 --> 00:10:27,460
Oh, benarkah?

205
00:10:28,002 --> 00:10:29,754
Ya, kalau begitu silakan datang perlahan.

206
00:10:29,838 --> 00:10:30,839
Ya

207
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,674
[Suara akhir panggilan]

208
00:10:32,757 --> 00:10:34,926
[♪ Variasi Bach Goldberg - Aria]

209
00:10:58,950 --> 00:11:00,827
[Orang-orang bersorak]

210
00:11:12,338 --> 00:11:13,256
[Haran] Hei, Kang Hyuk-chan

211
00:11:13,339 --> 00:11:15,383
Mengapa saya tidak dapat menghubungi Anda?

212
00:11:15,466 --> 00:11:18,094
[Hyukchan] Oh, maaf aku tidak menerimanya karena aku tertidur.

213
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,096
Apakah Anda menderita susah tidur?

214
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:23,683
Akhir-akhir ini, pola tidurku kacau dan waktu tidurku pun kacau.

215
00:11:23,766 --> 00:11:26,477
[Haran] Katanya lagu ini efektif untuk insomnia

216
00:11:26,561 --> 00:11:28,855
Dengarkan saat kamu tidak bisa tidur, oke?

217
00:11:35,904 --> 00:11:37,280
[Chan] Ayo, mundur!

218
00:11:37,363 --> 00:11:38,990
- Tiba-tiba? - [Chan] Ya

219
00:11:39,073 --> 00:11:40,617
[Man 1] Hei, haruskah kita memesan kebanggaan?

220
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:41,576
[Man 2] Bukankah bumbunya lebih enak?

221
00:11:41,659 --> 00:11:42,493
